03:07:32.505 --> 03:07:33.585
that as well, right?

3532
03:07:34.775 --> 03:07:36.345
Like there are, there are like,

3533
03:07:36.855 --> 03:07:39.505
there's an equivalent version of freedom of expression

3534
03:07:39.505 --> 03:07:41.625
that's granted to children by, um,

3535
03:07:41.955 --> 03:07:43.745
sorry I've forgotten the acronym for it at the moment,

3536
03:07:43.765 --> 03:07:45.545
but the kind of rights rights for children

3537
03:07:45.775 --> 03:07:46.785
that we have in New Zealand.

3538
03:07:48.285 --> 03:07:50.625
Um, thank you, uh, Vanessa Ween. Um, thank

3539
03:07:50.625 --> 03:07:51.625
You. Quick final question. Um,

3540
03:07:51.625 --> 03:07:53.545
you asked, um, well,

3541
03:07:53.545 --> 03:07:56.185
you pointed out that, um, there'll be, um,

3542
03:07:56.875 --> 03:07:58.225
trade off somewhere and it's,

3543
03:07:58.225 --> 03:07:59.825
which is the worst of the harms.

3544
03:07:59.885 --> 03:08:02.985
So do you think harms to adults of not being able

3545
03:08:02.985 --> 03:08:06.825
to express themselves freely, um, are greater than the harms

3546
03:08:07.005 --> 03:08:08.825
to children who are exploited online?

