could you just elaborate what you mean by that?

3549
03:08:18.015 --> 03:08:21.585
Like all of the online, um, sex exploitation that occurs,

3550
03:08:21.765 --> 03:08:24.345
um, or exposure to pornography

3551
03:08:24.685 --> 03:08:29.305
or, um, the harmful effects of, uh, the, uh,

3552
03:08:29.445 --> 03:08:33.745
way the algorithms work, um, on social media, um, various

