4982
04:48:15.865 --> 04:48:19.405
the harms young people face online include sexual abuse

4983
04:48:19.425 --> 04:48:22.725
by predators, including catfishing, early exposure

4984
04:48:22.745 --> 04:48:25.445
to pornography, leading to distorted views of sex,

4985
04:48:26.005 --> 04:48:28.835
heightened social anxiety due to fewer chances

4986
04:48:28.835 --> 04:48:30.715
