to raise a child is still true,

4999
04:49:03.245 --> 04:49:06.625
but today's village often lacks the strong community ties

5000
04:49:06.925 --> 04:49:11.025
or the large backyards that older generations once had.

5001
04:49:11.445 --> 04:49:14.945
The online world offers benefits to global connection,

5002
04:49:15.245 --> 04:49:18.465
access to information and platforms for advocacy.

5003
04:49:19.435 --> 04:49:20.965
When it comes to responsibility,

5004
04:49:21.445 --> 04:49:24.205
