for minimizing harm on the members'.

5012
04:49:39.765 --> 04:49:43.285
Bill proposing a ban on under 16 use of social media,

5013
04:49:43.605 --> 04:49:47.005
I would caution that an outright ban is a blunt instrument.

5014
04:49:47.625 --> 04:49:51.325
Unlike alcohol or smoking, which have no positive benefits,

5015
04:49:51.545 --> 04:49:53.965
social media can be valuable when used safely,

5016
04:49:54.765 --> 04:49:57.885
a ban risks pushing young people toward alternative,

5017
04:49:58.235 --> 04:50:00.125
potentially more dangerous channels.

5018
04:50:00.825 --> 04:50:03.085
