devices by default.

5025
04:50:19.755 --> 04:50:22.295
Number three, fund parenting education

5026
04:50:22.315 --> 04:50:24.895
and practical tools to support whanau and parents.

5027
04:50:25.355 --> 04:50:28.975
Number four, invest in a wide range of accessible,

5028
