the DIA's Digital Child Exploitation filtering system,

6423
06:10:51.055 --> 06:10:53.205
which includes blocking websites on the internet

6424
06:10:53.205 --> 06:10:54.245
Watch foundation list.

6425
06:10:54.665 --> 06:10:56.165
And we work with the banks and government

6426
06:10:56.165 --> 06:10:59.005
and law enforcement to identify and block scam websites.

6427
