6428
06:11:01.125 --> 06:11:03.085
hosting the shooters video immediately

6429
06:11:03.085 --> 06:11:04.725
after the Christchurch terrorist attacks.

6430
06:11:05.385 --> 06:11:08.085
But the problem with network filtering at its that is

6431
06:11:08.085 --> 06:11:10.525
that it's becoming increasingly ineffective.

6432
06:11:11.225 --> 06:11:13.485
So firstly, it can be easily circumvented

6433
06:11:13.505 --> 06:11:16.005
by motivated users using VPNs.

6434
06:11:16.145 --> 06:11:18.965
And these are very easy to access and use even for children.

6435
06:11:19.905 --> 06:11:21.805
And more and more websites are encrypted.

6436
06:11:21.905 --> 06:11:23.445
And what that means is that we can't see

6437
06:11:23.445 --> 06:11:25.325
what content people are accessing and

6438
06:11:25.325 --> 06:11:26.845
therefore we don't know which traffic to block.

6439
06:11:27.665 --> 06:11:30.645
And network level filtering is also a blunt tool in

6440
06:11:30.645 --> 06:11:32.925
that you have to block it the entire website level.

6441
06:11:33.225 --> 06:11:36.245
So this means it'd be necessary to block all of all

6442
06:11:36.245 --> 06:11:38.645
of YouTube, Instagram or TikTok

6443
06:11:38.715 --> 06:11:41.885
because we can't block individual pages or posts of concern.

6444
06:11:42.875 --> 06:11:46.165
However, if you were to look at doing network filtering,

6445
06:11:46.165 --> 06:11:48.045
there's a few things that we would, uh, need

6446
06:11:48.045 --> 06:11:51.765
to consider from a ISPs perspective to be in place, um,

6447
06:11:51.905 --> 06:11:53.045
in order for that legislation

6448
06:11:53.045 --> 06:11:54.405
to be effective from our point of view.

6449
06:11:54.505 --> 06:11:56.365
So the first is we'd need government direction.

6450
06:11:56.825 --> 06:11:58.725
So government needs to formally tell us

6451
06:11:59.265 --> 06:12:00.845
as network operators what to block.

6452
06:12:01.425 --> 06:12:03.205
The second is we'd need a trusted authority.

6453
06:12:03.425 --> 06:12:05.965
So a central and auditable authority needs

6454
06:12:05.965 --> 06:12:07.645
to make the decisions on what to block

6455
