especially when done at the network level.

6486
06:13:20.025 --> 06:13:21.885
It can only block entire websites

6487
06:13:21.945 --> 06:13:24.245
and can easily be avoided by motivated users.

6488
06:13:24.985 --> 06:13:28.245
Device level filtering is better as it offers more control,

